    <p class="hero-sub mb-0">Reach patients and families actively searching for treatment. Upgrade anytime.</p> 

</div> *@

<main class="page">

<section class="hero1">
        <span class="eyebrow">Advertise With Us</span>
        <h1>Help Treatment Seekers Find Your Facility</h1>
        <p>Start with a free listing, then choose the visibility level that fits your facility type, bed capacity, location, insurance mix, and admission goals.</p>
    </section>


<section class="claim-panel">
    <h2>It’s <span>free</span> to be listed</h2>
    <p>Search for your facility below. If it is not listed yet, submit your information and we will help you claim your profile.</p>
    <div class="search-box"><input type="text" placeholder="Your facility name"><button>Search</button></div>
</section>


<section class="dynamic-strip">
      <h2>Visibility depends on your <span>facility type and capacity</span></h2>
      <p>A 6-bed inpatient center does not need the same exposure as a large outpatient provider. Our pricing review estimates the visibility level needed based on real facility inputs.</p>
    </section>

 



<!-- Pricing Cards -->
<div class="container pb-2 px-4">
