                    <li><span class="check-dot check-gray"><i class="fa-solid fa-check check-icon" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>Directory listing</li>
                    <li><span class="check-dot check-gray"><i class="fa-solid fa-check check-icon" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>Basic profile information</li>
                    <li><span class="check-dot check-gray"><i class="fa-solid fa-check check-icon" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>Limited search visibility</li>
